{"tha-ap471:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap471:0.2":"Salakusumiyavagga ","tha-ap471:0.3":"9 Sayampatibhaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap471:1.1":"“Kakudham vilasantamva, ","tha-ap471:1.2":"devadevam narasabham; ","tha-ap471:1.3":"Rathiyam patipajjantam, ","tha-ap471:1.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:2.1":"Tamandhakaram nasetva, ","tha-ap471:2.2":"santaretva bahum janam; ","tha-ap471:2.3":"Nanalokena jotantam, ","tha-ap471:2.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:3.1":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap471:3.2":"niyantam lokanayakam; ","tha-ap471:3.3":"Uddharantam bahu satte, ","tha-ap471:3.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:4.1":"Ahanantam dhammabherim, ","tha-ap471:4.2":"maddantam titthiye gane; ","tha-ap471:4.3":"Sihanadam vinadantam, ","tha-ap471:4.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:5.1":"Yavata brahmalokato, ","tha-ap471:5.2":"agantvana sabrahmaka; ","tha-ap471:5.3":"Pucchanti nipune panhe, ","tha-ap471:5.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:6.1":"Yassanjalim karitvana, ","tha-ap471:6.2":"ayacanti sadevaka; ","tha-ap471:6.3":"Tena punnam anubhonti, ","tha-ap471:6.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:7.1":"Sabbe jana samagantva, ","tha-ap471:7.2":"sampavarenti cakkhumam; ","tha-ap471:7.3":"Na vikampati ajjhittho, ","tha-ap471:7.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:8.1":"Nagaram pavisato yassa, ","tha-ap471:8.2":"ravanti bheriyo bahu; ","tha-ap471:8.3":"Vinadanti gaja matta, ","tha-ap471:8.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:9.1":"Vithiya gacchato yassa, ","tha-ap471:9.2":"sabbabha jotate sada; ","tha-ap471:9.3":"Abbhunnata sama honti, ","tha-ap471:9.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:10.1":"Byaharantassa buddhassa, ","tha-ap471:10.2":"cakkavalampi suyyati; ","tha-ap471:10.3":"Sabbe satte vinnapeti, ","tha-ap471:10.4":"ko disva na pasidati. ","tha-ap471:11.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap471:11.2":"yam buddhamabhikittayim; ","tha-ap471:11.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap471:11.4":"kittanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap471:12.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap471:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap471:12.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap471:13.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap471:13.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap471:13.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap471:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap471:14.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap471:14.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap471:15.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sayampatibhaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap471:16.1":"Sayampatibhaniyattherassapadanam navamam. "}